<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久很久以前，有一位善良的妇人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很喜欢在花园里忙碌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的名字叫玛丽戈尔德。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她过着非常俭朴的生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她只有一个愿望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我能有个孩子。”她叹息道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天早上，她很早就起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她往窗外看，发现了一件奇怪的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么我的花朵摇摆得这么厉害？”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走到外面去看个究竟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！这是什么？”她吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雏菊丛里站着一个提着篮子的小精灵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的双颊通红，背上有小小的翅膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她往上看，看到玛丽戈尔德夫人正在俯视着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别踩我！”她高声叫，“我不是虫子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是仙女吗？”玛丽戈尔德夫人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了。”她指着自己的翅膀回答，“我是一个花园仙女。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在这里做什么？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来帮你管理花园，”仙女说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我要走了，我已经待太长时间了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等，你可以帮我实现一个愿望吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽戈尔德夫人兴奋地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仙女转了转眼睛，“我又不是一个精灵。”她尖锐地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138547</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，她注意到玛丽戈尔德夫人伤心的表情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，好吧，我看看我能不能帮上你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是你要答应我，不会对其他人说起我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽戈尔德夫人答应了，并说：“我想要一个孩子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仙女想了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从篮子里拿出了一个东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个特别的种子。”仙女说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把它种在花盆里。把花盆放在窗户边。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要浇水。它只需要大量的阳光。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要等几天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽戈尔德夫人仔细地看着种子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抬起头问：“然后呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是仙女已经飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽戈尔德夫人把种子带回家，按照仙女的话做了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>种子长得很快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久后，它就长出了一个郁金香花苞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第三天早上，玛丽戈尔德夫人发现花苞在动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“正在发生什么事情呢。”她小声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽戈尔德夫人弯下腰，亲吻了一下花苞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，花瓣一片接着一片地打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽戈尔德夫人惊讶地盯着花朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的愿望终于实现了！”她大声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个非常小的女孩在花朵中央。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的头发是阳光的颜色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的眼睛是大海的蓝色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在哪里？”女孩儿问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的声音非常动听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是你的家。”玛丽戈尔德夫人说，“我是你的妈妈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽戈尔德伸出她的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小女孩儿跳进她的手掌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈。”小女孩说，“我叫什么名字？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小女孩只有玛丽戈尔德夫人的大拇指那么大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽戈尔德夫人擦了擦眼泪，说道：“你的名字是拇指姑娘。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>